    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, a definitive example of Bavarian engineering. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. This vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance: the dual-VANOS unit has been rebuilt with Beisan components, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to prevent floor pan fatigue. The suspension geometry remains true, utilizing original bushings and Sachs dampers for a factory-spec dampening profile. The exterior displays impeccable paint depth with no swirl marks or rock chips, while the interior Nappa leather remains supple with no bolster wear. A true turn-key enthusiast vehicle with a meticulously documented service file.",
